data.description: Beautiful custom home with detached Casita. 3 Car Garage with epoxy floor.  Home is full of upgrades. Open and spacious floor plan with a large kitchen and beautiful granite throughout home. Custom cabinets with oversized trim. Tile and new hardwood floor. High end hardware. A spacious laundry room can also be a craft room. Walk in closets. Fully walled and private yard. Meticulous landscaping front and back. Garden area.  Storage room climate controlled attached to house. Great Cul-de-sac location. No HOA. Security system. R/O and Water Softner. Double Oven. Plumbed for central Vac. Energy efficient window coverings. Hardwood floors in Master and closet. Spacious master closet. Added Rain gutters around the whole house.
data.whatILove: Comfy Casita in a Quiet well maintained neighborhood. Close to parks and shopping and bike trails. Great freeway access. Abundance of off street parking. Raised vegetable garden. Water fountain feature.
